OL,3,CSimon Cowell 'devastated' and
OL,4,C'heartbroken' at death of Liam Payne
OL,6,FThe music mogul said he feels "empty"
OL,7,Fin a now-deleted statement posted on
OL,8,FInstagram following the death of the
OL,9,Fformer One Direction member.
OL,11,FSimon Cowell has said he is
OL,12,F"devastated" after the death of One
OL,13,FDirection star Liam Payne, adding
OL,14,F"every tear I have shed is a memory
OL,15,Ffor you".
OL,17,FPayne's girlfriend, Kate Cassidy, also
OL,18,Ftook to social media to say she loved
OL,19,Fhim "unconditionally and completely"
OL,20,Fand that she has been at a "complete
OL,21,Floss" since his death.
