OL,6,FIn a statement posted on Instagram,
OL,7,Fshe said: "Thank you for all of the
OL,8,Fkind words and love that has been sent
OL,9,Fmy way. I have been at a complete
OL,10,Floss. Nothing about the past few days
OL,11,Fhave felt real.
OL,13,F"I ask and pray that you'll give me
OL,14,Fthe space to navigate this in private.
OL,15,FLiam, my angel, you are everything. I
OL,16,Fwant you to know I loved you
OL,17,Funconditionally and completely. I will
OL,18,Fcontinue to love you for the rest of
OL,19,Fmy life. I love you Liam. "
