OL,3,CSimon Cowell 'devastated' and
OL,4,C'heartbroken' at death of Liam Payne
OL,6,FCowell posted a tribute to the former
OL,7,Fboy band star on his Instagram account
OL,8,Fon Friday evening, before deleting it
OL,9,Fminutes later and then reposting it.
OL,11,F"You never really know how you feel
OL,12,Fabout someone until a moment like this
OL,13,Fhappens," he said in a statement on
OL,14,FInstagram. "Liam, I am devastated.
OL,15,FHeartbroken. And I feel empty.
OL,17,F"And I want you to know how much love
OL,18,Fand respect I have for you. Every tear
OL,19,FI have shed is a memory for you.
