OL,3,CSimon Cowell 'devastated' and
OL,4,C'heartbroken' at death of Liam Payne
OL,6,F"This is so difficult to put into
OL,7,Fwords right now. I went outside today
OL,8,Fand I thought about so many times we
OL,9,Fhad together. I wanted to let you know
OL,10,Fwhat I would always say to the
OL,11,Fthousands of people who would always
OL,12,Fask me. What is Liam like?
OL,14,F"And I would tell them you were kind,
OL,15,Ffunny, sweet, thoughtful, talented,
OL,16,Fhumble, focused. And how much you
OL,17,Floved music. And how much love you
OL,18,Fgenuinely had for the fans."
