OL,6,FCowell continued: "I had to tell you
OL,7,Fwhen you were 14 that this wasn't your
OL,8,Ftime. And we both made a promise that
OL,9,Fwe would meet again. A lot of people
OL,10,Fwould have given up. You didn't.
OL,12,F"You came back and within months the
OL,13,Fwhole world know Liam. And you never
OL,14,Fforgot the fans. I watched you
OL,15,Fspending so much time with people who
OL,16,Fhad wanted to meet you. You really
OL,17,Fcared.
