OL,3,CSimon Cowell 'devastated' and
OL,4,C'heartbroken' at death of Liam Payne
OL,6,F"You came to see me last year. Not for
OL,7,Fa meeting. Just to sit and talk. And
OL,8,Fwe reminisced about all of the fun
OL,9,Ftimes we had together. And how proud
OL,10,Fyou were to be a dad."
OL,12,FThe statement continued: "After you
OL,13,Fleft, I was reminded that you were
OL,14,Fstill the sweet, kind boy I had met
OL,15,Fall of those years ago. I have met
OL,16,Fyour son, Bear. He has your smile and
OL,17,Fthat twinkle in his eye that you have.
