OL,6,F"He will be so proud of everything you
OL,7,Fachieved. And how you achieved it. I
OL,8,Falways thought the 5 of you in the
OL,9,Fband as brothers. And regarding their
OL,10,Fmessages today I believe you were.
OL,12,F"And now Liam, I can see the effect
OL,13,Fyou had on so many people because you
OL,14,Fleft us too soon. Rest in peace my
OL,15,Ffriend. And I am sending my love,
OL,16,Fthoughts and prayers to your family."
