OL,6,FIt comes after his former bandmates
OL,7,Fposted a joint statement, saying they
OL,8,Fare "completely devastated" by the
OL,9,Floss of their "brother". It was the
OL,10,Ffirst post on the band's Instagram
OL,11,Faccount in four years.
